BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Frosé Fridays
DTSTART:20260403T000000
DTEND:20260403T000000
UID:085173918d72e35767f91364ffdc3000@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:With all this warm weather lately\, we’ve got the perfect th
 ing for you to cool off with at our Tasting Room in Downtown Petaluma. Our
  winemaker\, Garrett Martin\, has crafted a refreshing new Frosé (frozen 
 rosé) made from our very own 2024 Sonoma County Rosé . We hope you love 
 it! Join us every Friday to enjoy a glass of frosé or any of our other aw
 ard-winning wines in the heart of Petaluma. Whether you’re exploring win
 e country\, planning a weekend outing\, or looking for the best frosé in 
 Sonoma County\, Adobe Road Winery is your go-to destination. Even better\,
  Inside Track Wine Club members enjoy additional club member pricing as we
 ll. Our frosé is available on Fridays\, while supplies last. Walk-ins wel
 come\, reservations recommended. Call or text (707) 774-6699 or use Tock t
 o reserve online.
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/frose-fridays/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
