BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Butter & Egg Days Parade & Festival
DTSTART:20260418T000000
DTEND:20260418T000000
UID:e4827a63cbabc1e966322a18d2e5f72b@adoberoadwines.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the 43nd Annual Butter & Egg Days Parade & Festiva
 l \, a celebration of Petaluma’s history\, creativity\, and community sp
 irit. See Downtown Petaluma to life with over 100 festive entries\, includ
 ing floats\, performances\, and local showcases. The parade starts at noon
 . After the parade\, visit our tasting room to unwind with a glass of wine
  or a tasting flight — because no celebration is complete without great 
 wine. See you in downtown Petaluma!
LOCATION:Adobe Road Tasting Room\, 6 Petaluma Blvd. N - Suite A1 Petaluma\
 , CA
URL:https://adoberoadwines.com/events/butter-and-egg-days-parade-2026/
X-SOURCE:Adobe Road Winery
END:VEVENT
